00:19:53,770 --> 00:19:55,120
Come!

247
00:19:55,120 --> 00:19:57,090
Chun Hua?

248
00:19:57,090 --> 00:19:59,040
Chun Hua, open the door!

249
00:20:00,800 --> 00:20:02,360
Chun Hua?

250
00:20:05,570 --> 00:20:06,780
Chun Hua?

251
00:20:06,780 --> 00:20:10,140
It is now your turn to save me.

252
00:20:11,820 --> 00:20:14,390
This is not the appropriate time to say something like that.

253
00:20:14,390 --> 00:20:16,340
Chun Hua, open the door!

254
00:20:17,660 --> 00:20:21,020
Calm down, Young Chief Master! It could be that Miss Chun Hua is in deep sleep.

255
00:20:21,020 --> 00:20:23,220
I'll go in to check.

256
00:20:24,500 --> 00:20:27,830
Miss Chun Hua, please forgive my discourtesy.

257
00:20:30,570 --> 00:20:34,720
Miss Chun Hua, Young Chief Master heard you scream in pain and feared your poison worsens.

258
00:20:34,720 --> 00:20:37,190
He sent me to check on you.

259
00:20:37,930 --> 00:20:39,950
Are you okay?

260
00:20:40,710 --> 00:20:44,290
Nothing is wrong with me, everything is fine.

261
00:20:44,290 --> 00:20:47,970
You all know that my illness comes and goes very sudden.

262
00:20:47,970 --> 00:20:52,630
Just now, I was probably having a nightmare.

263
00:20:54,260 --> 00:20:55,940
I was so scared.

264
00:20:55,940 --> 00:20:58,900
Do you know that you scared Young Chief Master to death?

265
00:21:18,130 --> 00:21:20,270
Since you are okay,

266
00:21:21,120 --> 00:21:23,470
I wish you a restful sleep.

267
00:21:41,730 --> 00:21:43,940
I was so scared!

268
00:21:47,550 --> 00:21:50,220
Are you worried about me?

269
00:21:50,220 --> 00:21:53,270
Don't worry! I still need to take care of you.

270
00:21:55,050 --> 00:21:59,110
I should have opened the door and let them kill you just now!

271
00:22:00,200 --> 00:22:02,450
You would not dare.

272
00:22:04,780 --> 00:22:09,610
Do you want them to find us in bed together?

273
00:22:15,970 --> 00:22:18,020
Pervert!

274
00:22:21,610 --> 00:22:23,840
Feng Caicai is a good girl.

275
00:22:23,840 --> 00:22:25,650
So let her know some good news.

276
00:22:25,650 --> 00:22:28,560
Tell her that Li Yu is not Master Shi.

277
00:22:31,340 --> 00:22:33,970
Three days later, Bu'er will invite you to a banquet.

278
00:22:33,970 --> 00:22:37,280
There will be Soft Muscle Powder in all of the food.
(TN: a poison from Western Regions first appeared in "Evening Heaven and Slaying the Dragon." It's colorless and fragrant, making the whole body becomes sore and weak.)

279
00:22:37,280 --> 00:22:40,580
Xiao Chun Hua, you should not eat too much.

280
00:22:40,580 --> 00:22:43,660
If you are poisoned again,

281
00:22:43,660 --> 00:22:46,580
I will be unable to save you.

282
00:23:16,300 --> 00:23:18,250
You sure have nerve.

283
00:23:19,610 --> 00:23:22,780
Do you think I don't guard against people from behind?

284
00:23:25,910 --> 00:23:27,250
I dare not.

285
00:23:27,250 --> 00:23:30,980
I didn't know Master was still here.

286
00:23:31,640 --> 00:23:35,340
However, having nerve is not always a bad thing.

287
00:23:35,340 --> 00:23:38,110
Now, Xiao Chun Hua will not think

288
00:23:38,110 --> 00:23:40,200
that I was trying to harm anyone.

289
00:23:41,080 --> 00:23:45,850
Master, everyone from Qianyue Cave has gathered outside Baxian Town.

290
00:23:45,850 --> 00:23:47,590
However, the martial arts circle show a huge power strength.

291
00:23:47,590 --> 00:23:50,840
What we had done, has caught their attention.

292
00:23:51,530 --> 00:23:53,190
It doesn't matter.

293
00:23:53,190 --> 00:23:56,210
Qianyue Cave will want to be in the clear this time around.

294
00:23:56,210 --> 00:23:58,560
We need to let the martial arts circle know

295
00:23:58,560 --> 00:24:01,500
who controls the situation in the pugilist world

296
00:24:01,500 --> 00:24:05,340
and who has let them act freely without hindrance.

297
00:24:06,110 --> 00:24:08,620
What news is there from Fengming Mountain Manor?

298
00:24:09,280 --> 00:24:13,660
They are troubled by clues to Master Shi's identity.

299
00:24:14,180 --> 00:24:15,830
So annoying!

300
00:24:15,830 --> 00:24:19,850
Should I personally help them if they are this weak?

301
00:24:20,450 --> 00:24:24,170
The day after tomorrow, Bu'er will raise a big uproar to entertain the martial arts circle.

302
00:24:24,170 --> 00:24:27,720
By then, if Xiao Bai still hasn't noticed that something is wrong,

303
00:24:27,720 --> 00:24:31,510
I fear that it will affect Miss Chun Hua negatively.

304
00:24:31,510 --> 00:24:36,550
It doesn't have a lot of time but many sects still harbor evil intent.

305
00:24:36,550 --> 00:24:39,740
So we don't know what trouble will be brewed up.

306
00:24:39,740 --> 00:24:45,020
Ye Yan, if we have a battle, you must be prepared first.

307
00:24:45,800 --> 00:24:49,050
If all goes smoothly that day,

308
00:24:49,050 --> 00:24:51,760
I will be able to take Xiao Chun Hua back to Qianyue Cave.

309
00:24:51,760 --> 00:24:53,410
Yes.

310
00:24:54,310 --> 00:24:56,220
I just want to beg you, Master,

311
00:24:56,220 --> 00:24:59,880
you should better go to a safer place for the time being.

312
00:25:00,560 --> 00:25:03,290
Safer place?

313
00:25:03,290 --> 00:25:08,200
Xiao Chun Hua is nervous about her poison everyday.

314
00:25:10,030 --> 00:25:11,980
It doesn't matter.

315
00:25:38,840 --> 00:25:41,210
Miss Chun Hua,

316
00:25:41,210 --> 00:25:43,920
I'm checking Baxian Residence accounts.

317
00:25:49,480 --> 00:25:53,120
Miss Caicai, how is your investigation?

318
00:25:53,120 --> 00:25:57,170
Now, we have two suspects. One is the disciple of Baxian Residence, Li Yu.

319
00:25:57,170 --> 00:26:00,130
The other one is his master, Bu'er.

320
00:26:01,030 --> 00:26:03,450
Li Yu is not Master Shi.

321
00:26:04,310 --> 00:26:06,950
Miss Chun Hua, how are you so sure?

322
00:26:07,860 --> 00:26:11,250
However, what you said is logical.

323
00:26:11,250 --> 00:26:16,690
Young Master Qin found out that the landlady of the restaurant is the mother of Li Yu.

324
00:26:16,690 --> 00:26:20,910
She was pregnant in the brothel before so she got kicked out.

325
00:26:20,910 --> 00:26:23,020
The Healer took her in.

326
00:26:23,020 --> 00:26:26,110
Li Yu was naughty when he was young. Others deluded him so he became a gambler.

327
00:26:26,110 --> 00:26:30,430
It's also the Healer who corrected and got him out from gambling; thus, he became his disciple.

328
00:26:30,430 --> 00:26:34,670
I never imagined they have such a sad past.

329
00:26:35,170 --> 00:26:40,150
Since it was like this, those two would appreciate the Healer.

330
00:26:40,150 --> 00:26:42,440
If they weren't threatened by others,

331
00:26:42,440 --> 00:26:46,210
they wouldn't do evil with the Healer's skills.

332
00:26:46,210 --> 00:26:47,490
You are right.

333
00:26:47,490 --> 00:26:50,360
Moreover, Li Yu's life currently is also pitiful.

334
00:26:50,360 --> 00:26:52,840
He doesn't show any sign of wanting to get rich.

335
00:26:52,840 --> 00:26:56,460
As for this Bu'er, two years after the Healer died,

336
00:26:56,460 --> 00:26:59,660
his business has spread all over Baxian City.

337
00:27:00,150 --> 00:27:04,050
So are you saying that every piece of evidence

338
00:27:04,050 --> 00:27:07,060
all points to Master Bu'er?

339
00:27:15,390 --> 00:27:18,710
The most interesting thing is Li Yu surrendered to me yesterday.

340
00:27:18,710 --> 00:27:20,840
Bu'er, Bu'er.

341
00:27:21,830 --> 00:27:27,010
We probably need to seriously consider if he is Master Shi.

342
00:27:28,050 --> 00:27:31,170
This deduction is very convincing indeed.

343
00:27:31,170 --> 00:27:33,340
However...

344
00:27:33,340 --> 00:27:35,730
Bu'er seems to be very nice.

345
00:27:35,730 --> 00:27:38,510
I really can't believe it.

346
00:27:38,510 --> 00:27:42,920
We didn't expect human's greed and darkness would pan out to be like this.

347
00:27:42,920 --> 00:27:47,210
It's just that by selling the Longevity fruit, he should have become rich already.

348
00:27:47,210 --> 00:27:49,480
However, after checking the accounts for a long time,

349
00:27:49,480 --> 00:27:51,890
I didn't find any abruptly change.

350
00:27:52,590 --> 00:27:56,490
Hence, these can't become evidence.

351
00:28:00,720 --> 00:28:03,760
Greed and stinginess are two sides of one thing.

352
00:28:04,330 --> 00:28:06,690
Bu'er accumulated wealth through unfair means

353
00:28:06,690 --> 00:28:10,510
but that still does not mean he plans to spend all that money.

354
00:28:10,510 --> 00:28:15,430
I suspect he might have hidden his wealth somewhere.

355
00:28:15,430 --> 00:28:18,790
This is his seized fortune after all. Yes!

356
00:28:18,790 --> 00:28:21,750
Furthermore, the place he hid it

357
00:28:21,750 --> 00:28:25,840
must be somewhere that he can reach easily and get to quickly,

358
00:28:25,840 --> 00:28:29,810
then he could feel at ease.

359
00:28:29,810 --> 00:28:33,810
Miss Chun Hua, do you mean that his precious fortune

360
00:28:33,810 --> 00:28:36,130
is hidden in the Baxian Residence?

361
00:28:37,590 --> 00:28:41,530
I think a person like Bu'er would definitely believe

362
00:28:41,530 --> 00:28:46,190
that the more public a place is, indeed the safer it is.

363
00:29:02,980 --> 00:29:05,130
What you said makes sense.

364
00:29:06,270 --> 00:29:09,750
Then, Miss Chun Hua, why don't you stay and rest here?

365
00:29:22,660 --> 00:29:26,070
[Baxian Residence]

366
00:29:35,350 --> 00:29:37,360
Baxian Residence is not big.

367
00:29:37,360 --> 00:29:40,510
It should be easy to find these stolen treasures.

368
00:29:40,510 --> 00:29:42,100
I even searched the aisles.

369
00:29:42,100 --> 00:29:45,980
The inside is empty and there is no space to store things.

370
00:29:46,460 --> 00:29:48,440
This is where the problem lies.

371
00:29:48,440 --> 00:29:52,930
We spent so many hours but there is no clue at all.

372
00:29:53,530 --> 00:29:57,000
That's right, Miss Feng! Why didn't Young Chief Master come with you?

373
00:29:57,000 --> 00:29:59,880
He is still troubled by Miss Chun Hua's poison.

374
00:29:59,880 --> 00:30:02,750
All day, he is racking his brain for answers.

375
00:30:02,750 --> 00:30:04,970
However, Miss Chun Hua and Shangguan Qiu Yue clearly have—

376
00:30:04,970 --> 00:30:07,220
Young Chief Master likes Miss Chun Hua.

377
00:30:07,220 --> 00:30:10,060
Miss Chun Hua is coincidentally here.

378
00:30:10,060 --> 00:30:13,570
We shouldn't rain on his parade (spoil his joy).

379
00:30:13,570 --> 00:30:16,140
Besides, I predict that

380
00:30:16,140 --> 00:30:19,980
the bird I saw yesterday was indeed Shangguan Qiu Yue's.

381
00:30:19,980 --> 00:30:21,630
How do you know?

382
00:30:22,450 --> 00:30:25,660
The mark I saw on Miss Chun Hua's palm today

383
00:30:25,660 --> 00:30:28,200
is deeper in color now.

384
00:30:28,200 --> 00:30:30,220
We cannot continue like this anymore.

385
00:30:30,220 --> 00:30:33,860
Shangguan Qiu Yue cannot be by Miss Chun Hua's side for much longer.

386
00:30:33,860 --> 00:30:38,190
No good will come from this for Chun Hua or the Young Chief Master.

387
00:30:38,190 --> 00:30:42,300
Maybe it will even cause more trouble.

388
00:30:43,580 --> 00:30:47,060
Miss Feng, we meet again!

389
00:30:58,330 --> 00:31:03,150
This Li Yu seems to have fallen for our Caicai.

390
00:31:03,150 --> 00:31:06,350
This brat really has some guts.

391
00:31:06,350 --> 00:31:08,280
However...

392
00:31:12,800 --> 00:31:16,160
You still have me and I have you.

393
00:31:28,100 --> 00:31:32,560
Did you look for me for something earlier?

394
00:31:32,560 --> 00:31:36,140
You came at the right time as I have some questions for you.

395
00:31:36,140 --> 00:31:38,670
I will answer without reserve.

396
00:31:39,540 --> 00:31:42,460
You has come to Baxian Residence for over a year.

397
00:31:42,460 --> 00:31:46,100
Do you know where to store goods here?

398
00:31:50,060 --> 00:31:53,130
Although I was manipulated and instructed by Master Bu'er,

399
00:31:53,130 --> 00:31:55,490
