00:31:55,490 --> 00:31:58,970
He just forced me to do some menial, dirty work.

401
00:31:58,970 --> 00:32:01,460
He keeps everything else private.

402
00:32:01,460 --> 00:32:03,700
This kind of person worships money like his life.

403
00:32:03,700 --> 00:32:07,370
There's no way he'd willingly give away his precious things to another person.

404
00:32:07,370 --> 00:32:11,940
