Do you know what quirks Master Bu'er has?

408
00:32:31,470 --> 00:32:33,640
He doesn't like the company of women.

409
00:32:33,640 --> 00:32:35,530
He does not like alcohol.

410
00:32:35,530 --> 00:32:39,150
