415
00:32:52,610 --> 00:32:54,770
Tell me quickly!

416
00:32:58,090 --> 00:32:59,990
Bu'er has a very interesting habit.

417
00:32:59,990 --> 00:33:02,260
He likes to sweep this hallway himself.

418
00:33:02,260 --> 00:33:05,090
He does it three times a day at least.

419
00:33:05,090 --> 00:33:07,230
I do not know if it is just a habit,

420
00:33:07,230 --> 00:33:10,370
